This Privacy Policy (“
Privacy Policy
”) details how your Personal Information collected via the Site and/or App is used and processed by Boards.
BY ENTERING, ACCESSING OR USING THE SITE AND/OR APP AND/OR SERVICES AND/OR BY PROVIDING PERSONAL INFORMATION TO US,  YOU AGREE TO THE TERMS AND CONDITIONS SET FORTH IN THIS PRIVACY POLICY, INCLUDING TO THE COLLECTION AND PROCESSING OF YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION (AS DEFINED BELOW). IF YOU DISAGREE TO ANY TERM PROVIDED HEREIN, YOU MAY NOT ACCESS OR USE THE SITE AND/OR APP AND/OR SERVICES AND YOU SHOULD NOT PROVIDE US WITH ANY PERSONAL INFORMATION.
FOR AVOIDANCE OF DOUBT, YOU HEREBY CONSENT TO THE COLLECTION, PROCESSING, TRANSFER AND USE OF YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION. YOU ALSO ACKNOWLEDGE AND CONFIRM THAT YOU ARE NOT REQUIRED TO PROVIDE US WITH YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION AND THAT SUCH INFORMATION IS VOLUNTARILY PROVIDED TO US.
Note to non-EU or UK based Users:
BY ENTERING, CONNECTING TO, ACCESSING OR USING THE SITE AND/OR APP AND/OR SERVICES, YOU ACKNOWLEDGE THAT YOU ARE OR HAVE HAD THE OPPORTUNITY TO BECOME AWARE OF AND AGREE TO BOARDS’ PRACTICES DESCRIBED HEREIN, INCLUDING THE PROCESSING (INCLUDING COLLECTING, USING, DISCLOSING, RETAINING OR DISPOSING) OF YOUR INFORMATION UNDER THE TERMS OF THIS POLICY.
